{"tid":2069321,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國一個小組倡否決將跨太平洋光纖電網連結香港","createTime":"2020-06-18T09:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T10:15:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"634dc9ae52bf696a2cce651fca3620259df521e4","tid":2069321,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:42:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532801-20200618.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532801-20200618.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=ccb1cbb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532801-20200618.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=07b561c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532801-20200618.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國一個特別電訊小組以國家安全為由，建議聯邦通信委員會否決「跨太平洋海底光纖網」連結香港的申請，改為只是連接台灣及菲律賓。<br />\n<br />\n有關光纖網長12800公里，2016年由Google、Facebook及其他公司合作建議鋪設，以提高互聯網速度及容量，但其中一間公司與中國電信服務商「鵬博士電信集團」有關，擔心如果海底電纜連接香港，可能會令北京得以收集數以百萬計美國人的敏感個人數據。<br />\n<br />\n小組聲明又說，中國政府近期為取消香港自治的行動，以及可能容許中國情報與國安部門在香港活動，亦加深當局對美國國家安全的擔憂。"},{"pid":"e5da5d8bc4e672a1d8c9d40d4bfc3b1c588c8222","tid":2069321,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187e2b196b8bf72d2b25af954caf814ddd2db4f5","tid":2069321,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"喜迎一國一制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11e50e0ffe31f332b24746af2f86fe4f25f1114","tid":2069321,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"正!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc916f088cdf54e535e182a7ad48f429247b8333","tid":